        {
            "title": "方舟健客料去年扭虧為盈 收入預計增30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">方舟健客(06086)發盈喜，預期2025年度將扭虧為盈，錄得淨利潤約700萬至1000萬元(人民幣．下同)，較2024年度虧損8.55億元大幅改善。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司又估計，去年收入將介乎35億至35.5億元，按年增長約30%，主要因為公司吸引了更多患者與醫生加入平台，令面向消費者的業務分部持續增長；至於扭虧為盈則由於收入增長，加上以權益結算以股份為基礎的交易減少。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611425-%e6%96%b9%e8%88%9f%e5%81%a5%e5%ae%a2%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e6%89%ad%e8%99%a7%e7%82%ba%e7%9b%88-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e9%a0%90%e8%a8%88%e5%a2%9e30",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/06086.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:59:20",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑芝麻智能配股認購方改變",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">黑芝麻智能(02533)公布，1月8 日訂立的配股協議，與認購C方的配售協議終止，改為向配予Shanghai Daixu Venture Capital Parnershi配售856.3萬股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shanghai Daixu Venture Capital Parnershi由戴思元實益擁有。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售完成後，董事長、執行董事及首席執行官單記章持股13.6%，戴思元持股4.57%，另一認購者嘉興信燦股6.85%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司月初公布配股，配股價18.88元，較上交易日聯交所收市價每股21.76元折讓約13.24%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611408-%e9%bb%91%e8%8a%9d%e9%ba%bb%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e6%96%b9%e6%94%b9%e8%ae%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251203_FI_source-web_02533-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:52:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "瑞和數智折讓近14%配股籌1.24億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">瑞和數智(03680)公布，擬配股集資約1.24億元；配股價0.783元，較該股上周五收市價0.91元折讓約13.96%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"瑞和數智官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"瑞和數智官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">瑞和數智官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股前5個交易日平均收迌價0.978元計，配股價較之折讓19.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資所得淨額約1.23億元，約70%用於償還借款及補充一般營運資金，餘下約30%用於戰略投資，但不包括直接或間接投資於加密貨幣或其他基於加密貨幣的資產投資。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611407-%e7%91%9e%e5%92%8c%e6%95%b8%e6%99%ba%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%9114%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c1-24%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/03680-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:45:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "昇能折讓17.82%配股籌1890萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">昇能集團(02459)公布，擬配股集資約1890萬元；配股價0.083元，較該股上周五收市價0.101元折讓17.82%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"昇能集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02459-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"昇能集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02459-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">昇能集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價0.1034元計，配股價較之折讓9.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資淨額約1840萬元，約50%用於發展石墨電極業務，包括但不限於採購原材料及石墨電極、支付分包及轉換成本及其他經營及管理費用；約50%將用於補充流動資金及作一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611397-%e6%98%87%e8%83%bd%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9317-82%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c1890%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_02459.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:39:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "國泰君安國際發盈喜 料去年純利升最少2.65倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國泰君安國際(01788)發盈喜，預期2025年全年淨利潤約介乎12.8億至13.8億元，較2024年度的3.51億元飆升2.65倍至2.93倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"國泰君安國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01778-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"國泰君安國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/01778-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">國泰君安國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，去年盈利提升，主要因為公司的企業融資、財富管理、資產管理及交易及投資等核心業務收入，均大幅上升，其中股權融資及經紀業務表現尤為突出。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611387-%e5%9c%8b%e6%b3%b0%e5%90%9b%e5%ae%89%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%912-65%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240717_FI_source-web_01778.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:34:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期夜水齊高水約20點 重磅港股ADR升多於跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時21分跌18點或0.07%，報15584點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26773點，較香港上日現貨收市高24點或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣598.1元，較上日香港收市高3.11元或0.52%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣168.8元，較上日香港收市高0.31元或0.19%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣97.7元，較上日香港收市高0.17元或0.18%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣116.3元，較上日香港收市高1.52元或1.32%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣36.3元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣130.9元，較上日香港收市高0.88元或0.68%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣83.1元，較上日香港收市高0.02元或0.02%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣421.8元，較上日香港收市低0.16元或0.04%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣67.2元，較上日香港收市高0.24元或0.36%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.6元，較上日香港收市低0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26772點，升54點，較上日恒指收市26749點，高水22點。科指期貨夜市收報5789點，較上日科指收市低水9點；國指期貨夜市收報9169點，較上日國指收市高水8點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611378-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%b0%b4%e9%bd%8a%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%8420%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%8d%87%e5%a4%9a%e6%96%bc%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:27:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "銀價突破100美元創新高　金價破頂迫近5000美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15607940&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">黃金及白銀價格再創新高，經濟及政治局勢不確定，資金流入避險資產。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20170226_FI_gold-price_FB_source-web_-4-1-1-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨白銀價格突破每盎司100美元關口，曾觸及約102.85美元，升約7%，今年以來不足1個月時間累計升約44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價迫近每盎司5000美元關口，現貨金高見4989.61美元，升近1.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期金2月合約高見4991.4美元，收報4979.7美元，升66.3美元，升幅1.3%，本周累計升逾8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15607940-%e9%8a%80%e5%83%b9%e7%aa%81%e7%a0%b4100%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82%e8%bf%ab%e8%bf%915000%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source_licensed_shutterstock_2009158820.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:27:44",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股低收　德股本周跌約1.6%　結束8星期升勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15607932&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲股市普遍向下，市場持續評估格陵蘭問題引發的歐美貿易緊張局勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐盟執委會擬將對美國總額達930億歐元的報復性貿易措施暫緩期再延長6個月。另外，德國總理默茨表示，不能接受美國總統特朗普倡議的和平委員會，目前的設立形式。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利及西班牙股市跌幅較大，跌約0.6%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英法股市連升兩日後回軟，富時100指數收報10143點，跌6點；法國CAC指數收報8143點，跌5點，兩者都跌約0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數反覆向上，25000點關口阻力仍大，收報24900點，升44點，升幅約0.2%，連升兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德股本周累計跌約1.6%，結束8個星期升勢。英股跌0.9%，亦結束3星期升勢。法股跌1.4%，連跌兩星期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15607932-%e6%ad%90%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e3%80%80%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%841-6%e3%80%80%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f8%e6%98%9f%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%87%e5%8b%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:27:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指低收285點　納指升約0.3%　英特爾急挫17%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15607923&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股3大指數個別發展，但全星期累計都跌，市場注視貿易緊張局勢及地緣政治風險。另外，英特爾業績後急挫，導致投資風險胃納減弱。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"英特爾 Intel (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240802_FI_source-ap_Intel1_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"英特爾 Intel (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240802_FI_source-ap_Intel1_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">英特爾 Intel (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯指數最多跌420點，曾失守49000點關口，收市報49098點，跌285點，跌幅約0.6%，結束兩日升勢。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標普500指數及納斯達克指數則三連升，創1星期收市新高。標普指數收報6915點，升2點。納指收報23501點，升65點，升幅約0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾今季業績展望不及預期，並表示難以滿足人工智能(AI)數據中心對伺服器晶片需求，拖累股價急挫17%收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他科技股個別發展，Netflix反彈3%，微軟亦升逾3%，Nvidia、Meta、亞馬遜升1.5%至2%，蘋果及Alphabet偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">記憶體相關股份普遍自紀錄高位回調，Sandisk急挫近6%，希捷科技(Seagate)微跌，美光則升0.5%再創新高。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本周累計，道指跌逾0.5%，標普500指數跌約0.4%，納指跌0.1%，同樣都連跌兩星期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15607923-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6285%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%840-3%e3%80%80%e8%8b%b1%e7%89%b9%e7%88%be%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab17-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:20:39",
